title: Act As If
itunes:title: Act As If
description:
Episode 346 - If you did not hear the episode before this one, you will want to listen to it first. Now that you know who you want to become, you need to start acting like that person aka becoming that person. In this episode I will dive deeper into that topic so that you can become the person that you want to be in your future.
